                    <li id="yr-tab-abbr-btn"><a class="yr-nav-link" onclick="yrSwitchTab('yr-tab-abbr', this)" style="background-color:#e8f5e9; border-color:#c8e6c9; color:#2e7d32;">еҮҰж–№з•Ҙз§°</a></li>
                    <li id="yr-tab-med-adj-btn" style="display:none;"><a class="yr-nav-link" onclick="yrSwitchTab('yr-tab-med-adj', this)" style="background-color:#fce4ec; border-color:#f8bbd0; color:#c2185b;">и–¬еүӨиӘҝж•ҙеҠ з®—</a></li>
                    <li id="yr-tab-med-adj-2026-btn"><a class="yr-nav-link" onclick="yrSwitchTab('yr-tab-med-adj-2026', this)" style="background-color:#fce4ec; border-color:#f8bbd0; color:#c2185b; font-weight:bold;">вңЁ и–¬еүӨиӘҝж•ҙеҠ з®—(26е№ҙж”№е®ҡзүҲ)</a></li>
