                            <button id="btn-med-adj-recalc-2026" class="yr-btn yr-btn-outline-secondary" style="font-weight:bold; padding:8px 0; width:100%; font-size:13px;" onclick="calcMedAdj2026(true)">рҹ”„ еҶҚиЁҲз®—<br><span style="font-size:10px;">(ж•ҙзҗҶгҒӘгҒ—)</span></button>
