                                <label style="font-size:12px; cursor:pointer; margin-bottom:8px;"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-med-adj-req1-2026"> зҷӮйӨҠдёҠеҝ…иҰҒгҒӘжҢҮе°ҺгӮ’е®ҹж–Ҫ</label>
                                <label style="font-size:12px; cursor:pointer; margin-bottom:8px;"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-med-adj-req2-2026"> еӨҡиҒ·зЁ®йҖЈжҗәгҒ«гӮҲгӮӢи©•дҫЎгғ»е…ұжңүгӮ’е®ҹж–Ҫ</label>
                                <label style="font-size:12px; cursor:pointer;"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-med-adj-req4-2026"> йҖҖйҷўе…ҲгҒ®и–¬еұҖзӯүгҒёж–ҮжӣёгҒ«гӮҲгӮӢжғ…е ұйҖЈжҗәгӮ’е®ҹж–Ҫ <span style="color:#c62828;font-weight:bold;">(вҖ»26е№ҙгӮҲгӮҠеҝ…й Ҳ)</span></label>
                                <div id="req3-container-2026" style="display:none; background:#fff3cd; border:1px solid #ffecb5; border-left:4px solid #ffc107; padding:8px; border-radius:4px;">
